<div class="text-left text-medium bump-down">
	The logo and company information you enter here is visible on Sales Orders, Invoices,
	Purchase Orders and Reports. An email address is required to send Sales Orders, 
	Purchase Orders and Invoices to your customers and vendors via email. The email 
	address you enter is the "From" address.
</div>
